                    "type":"paragraph",
                    "text":"Maternity leave applies to expectant or new mothers who require time off for pregnancy, childbirth and childcare. The maternity leave comprises of statutory or extended leave depending upon the organization. Organizations that are supporting gender DEI are providing fully paid, partially paid, or unpaid maternity leave of varying time period exceeding legislative requirements."
